data.text: #jiangsu #wuxi #china #pegasus Watertown, the kingdom of the Hailan Group. The atmosphere is very good, like being in Europe and there are activities to do all day long, whether it's boat riding, horseback riding or shopping. There are many restaurants and includes branded clothing from a variety of group stores. There are many brands and many promotional products. You can stay here all day long.
